  MINERful-Reloaded repository for licensing).
* `tools/ProM/`: ProM Framework + bundled plugins — see
  https://promtools.org/ for individual plugin licences.

Bundling is for convenience of the BA-thesis reviewer; users redistributing
this repository are responsible for ensuring the upstream licences allow it.
